&lt;p&gt;Responsible to the Director of IM&amp;T and service line leads for the timely, efficient and effective programme management of major Trust projects, ensuring that the Trust’s strategic goals, corporate objectives and performance are achieved.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SWAST’s programmes and projects have a direct impact on the lives of people in the South West and are key to effective service delivery and support the digital transformation of the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is a permanent job share - 3 days/week (22.5 hours/week)&lt;/p&gt;
